Create a folder called node-docker-app
Open cmd then type the command : cd node-docker-app
Once u went into the node-docker-app directory, type the command : npm init
Then npm install --save express
After installation is done, open package.json and app.js file
In the app.js file, write the code
Save the file and then run the command : node app.js
Next, visit the site https://hub.docker.com/ and click on Explore. Type node in : search for great content
Click on node(Docker official image) and further right click on How To Use This Image
Open dockerfile file and write the necessary commands
Once u have finished writing your commands, save it and then run : docker build -t hello docker .
Now run the final command : docker run -it -p 8888:3000 hello-docker
